Usefulness of Extended-FAST (EFAST-Extended Focused Assessment with Sonography 
for Trauma) in critical care setting.

[Article in English, Portuguese]

Flato UA(1), Guimarães HP(2), Lopes RD(3), Valiatti JL(4), Flato EM(5), Lorenzo 
RG(6).

